{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setreverseproxy:headers:"]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setReverseProxy:headers:"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets a reverse proxy URL and optional custom HTTP headers for all SDK network requests."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setReverseProxy:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"url","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"headers:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSDictionary","text":"NSDictionary<NSString *,NSString *>","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"headers","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The full URL of your reverse proxy endpoint (e.g., “https:\/\/proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh”). Must not be nil or empty.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"url"},{"name":"headers","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Optional dictionary of custom HTTP headers. Pass nil if no custom headers are needed.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Routes all Pushwoosh SDK network requests through your own proxy server."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is useful for:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Enterprise security"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Route traffic through corporate proxies","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Regional compliance","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Ensure data flows through specific regions","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Network monitoring","type":"text"}]},{"text":": Inspect and log SDK traffic","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Firewall restrictions","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Work around corporate firewall rules"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The proxy must forward requests to the appropriate Pushwoosh API endpoints"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"while preserving all headers and request body content.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Settings are not persisted and must be set on every app start."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"URL must start with https:\/\/ or http:\/\/."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Custom headers are only applied when reverse proxy is active.","type":"text"}]},{"text":"Example","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Configure proxy for enterprise deployment:"}]},{"code":["class NetworkConfiguration {","","    func configureForEnterprise() {","        guard let proxyURL = Configuration.shared.pushwooshProxyURL else {","            return","        }","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(proxyURL, headers: nil)","","        Logger.info(\"Pushwoosh configured to use proxy: \\(proxyURL)\")","    }","","    func configureForRegion(_ region: Region) {","        switch region {","        case .eu:","            Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(","                \"https:\/\/eu-proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh\",","                headers: [\"X-Auth-Token\": \"your-token\"]","            )","        case .asia:","            Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(","                \"https:\/\/asia-proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh\",","                headers: nil","            )","        case .us:","            break \/\/ No proxy needed","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setReverseProxy:headers:","roleHeading":"Type Method","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setReverseProxy:headers:"}],"title":"setReverseProxy:headers:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setReverseProxy:headers:","kind":"identifier"}]},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setReverseProxy:headers:":{"title":"setReverseProxy:headers:","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setreverseproxy:headers:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setReverseProxy:headers:"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setReverseProxy:headers:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setReverseProxy:headers:","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets a reverse proxy URL and optional custom HTTP headers for all SDK network requests."}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","type":"topic","title":"PushwooshCore","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"}}}